Privacy Policy
Effective Date: July 9, 2025
App Name: Tap

1. Introduction
TapTest ("we", "our", or "us") respects your privacy. This Privacy Policy outlines how we collect, use, and protect information when you use our tap game available at https://taptest.netlify.app.

2. Information We Collect
We do not collect personal identification data such as your name, email address, or phone number.

However, we may collect or store the following non-personal data:

Tap Actions & Score: Number of taps, points earned, and session progress.

Device Data: Browser type, screen size, and device type for performance optimization.

Local Storage Usage: We use localStorage to save your tap score on your device (not on our servers).

3. How We Use Your Information
We use non-personal data to:

Display your score and progress.

Improve gameplay and app responsiveness.

Ensure an optimal experience across devices.

4. Third-Party Services
We currently do not use third-party analytics, advertising, or tracking services. If this changes, we will update this policy accordingly.

5. Children‚Äôs Privacy
TapTest is suitable for all ages and does not collect any personal data. If you believe a child has submitted personal information, please contact us so we can take necessary action.

6. Security
All gameplay data is stored locally on your browser using secure technologies. No game data is transmitted to external servers.

